From 86538adef158674900c9acabce0ec19553a0880d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Lokesh B V <Lokesh.BV@Arm.com>
Date: Sat, 21 Sep 2024 17:46:21 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 65/78] Platform/Sgi: Add ACPI tables for RDV3R1 platform

RDV3R1 is the next platform in the Arm's reference design platform
series. This is a dual chip platform that includes 28 CPUs. In
preparation for adding support for this platform, add the initial
set of ACPI tables and reuse of some existing ACPI tables as applicable to
this platform.

Signed-off-by: Vijayenthiran Subramaniam <vijayenthiran.subramaniam@arm.com>
Signed-off-by: Lokesh B V <Lokesh.BV@Arm.com>
Signed-off-by: Dhinesh Kumar Balu <dhineshkumar.balu@arm.com>
Change-Id: I0e5749450bd0566657c66368597bad619263e905
